---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="description" content="页面不存在 — AIRDB Team" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#ffffff" />
    <title>404 · 节点未找到 — AIRDB Team</title>
    <link rel="preload" href="/fonts/ibm-plex-mono-400-latin.woff2" as="font" type="font/woff2" crossorigin />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="site-header">
      <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="AIRDB Team 首页">
        <strong>AIRDB</strong><span>/</span><em>TEAM</em>
      </a>
      <span></span>
      <a class="header-action" href="/#people">浏览成员 <span aria-hidden="true">↘</span></a>
    </header>

    <main class="notfound">
      <div class="notfound-inner">
        <p class="notfound-code" aria-hidden="true">ERR 404 — NODE NOT FOUND</p>
        <h1>这个节点<br />不在网络中。</h1>
        <p class="notfound-copy">你要找的页面不存在，或者已经移动到了别的坐标。网络中的其他节点仍在正常运行。</p>
        <pre class="notfound-trace" aria-hidden="true">$ traceroute ./lost-node
1  airdb.team  <span>ok</span>
2  *  *  *  <b>404 — 请求的节点无响应</b></pre>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="button button-primary" href="/">返回首页 <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
          <a class="button button-quiet" href="/#people">认识网络中的人 <span aria-hidden="true">↘</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <a class="brand brand-footer" href="/"><strong>AIRDB</strong><span>/</span><em>TEAM</em></a>
      <p>Independent by design.<br />Connected by ambition.</p>
      <div><a href="/#people">成员目录</a><a href="/#capabilities">能力地图</a><a href="mailto:team@airdb.team">联系我们</a></div>
      <small>© 2026 AIRDB Team</small>
    </footer>
  </body>

  <style>
    .notfound { display: grid; place-items: center; min-height: calc(100svh - 74px - 220px); padding: 90px var(--gutter); }
    .notfound-inner { max-width: 780px; }
    .notfound-code { margin: 0; color: var(--blue); font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", monospace; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: .1em; }
    .notfound h1 { margin: 26px 0 0; font-size: clamp(52px, 7vw, 104px); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -.06em; line-height: 1; }
    .notfound-copy { max-width: 540px; margin: 26px 0 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .notfound-trace { margin: 34px 0 0; padding: 18px 22px; overflow-x: auto; border: 1px solid var(--ink); background: var(--pale); color: var(--ink); font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", monospace; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.9; }
    .notfound-trace span { color: var(--blue); }
    .notfound-trace b { color: var(--coral); font-weight: 600; }
    .notfound .hero-actions { margin-top: 40px; }
    @media (max-width: 680px) {
      .notfound { min-height: calc(100svh - 64px - 220px); padding-top: 64px; padding-bottom: 64px; }
    }
  </style>
</html>
